Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ビビりゃ負けるぜ
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.99,0:04:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fear him and you{\fscx50\fsp-2} {\fscx100\fax-0.2}'{\fax0\fsp0}ll die!
