Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次第に引き離されてゆく
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.87,0:20:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel no anxiety.
